page.title: 14A Typical Garden
page.content: My garden is a typical one.It goes all the way round the house and has a path through the middle.The garden has bushes at one end.There is a {stream}in my garden it is not very deep but it is muddy.There are lot of trees in my garden.They are very old like my house. The garden is about half an acre. It has a back yard,which is made of brick. There are two{apple trees}which are in the back yard. There are many plants and flowers and an old garage which is falling down.Most of the trees are willow trees,bending over towards the stream. There are about five flower beds in the garden and they are near the house.
